Adobe Flash Builder for PHP has "added" support for connection with PHP Data and Web services. It has integrated PHP debugging which is not there in the version without "For PHP". Obviously Flash Builder for PHP carries all the same capabilities as that of plain Flash Builder. For more information, visit the FAQ section of product on Adobe page, I'm sure you will get more descriptive answers there! ;-)
